# Microsoft Purview Compliance Services — Pricing

## Packages

### 1. Quick Start — $3,500
- Deploy 2 sensitivity labels + retention rule
- Basic DLP policy implementation
- Deployment scripts included

### 2. Standard — $9,500
- Design workshop
- 5 labels + 3 retention rules + 3 DLP templates
- Reporting + handover training

### 3. Enterprise Program — $22,000+
- Governance strategy
- Automated deployment + CI/CD
- Incident response + evidence packs
- 90-day support

---

## Optional Add-Ons

- Additional Labels → $400/label  
- Classification Rules → $1,250  
- SIEM Integration → $2,000  
- Monthly Managed Support → $2,500/month  

---

## Billing Terms

- 50% upfront, 50% on delivery
- Work delivered remotely unless agreed otherwise
- Enterprise SLAs available upon request
